              <span id="reviewTextContainer3325972005" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15182861943859784761">My rating on this one may have been affected by my mood. It’s been difficult to find a book that I just can’t put down. Also, I read the author’s other book, In an instant, and LOVED it. Maybe this one just couldn’t hold up. I liked this book, but didn’t love it. There really isn’t a single reason - maybe it just moved a little slowly. And the ending was somewhat anticlimactic. So this book was just meh for me, but it might have just been me. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


